      "content": "lol okay, I guess. but the log transform didnt really fix the distribution issue for the really extreme values. if i cant get the residuals to look normal, how much is this actually going to mess up the p-values and my overall model reliability?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "lol okay, I guess. but the log transform didnt really fix the distribution issue for the really extreme values. if i cant get the residuals to look normal, how much is this actually going to mess up the p-values and my overall model reliability?",
